nodes.text: Rian Vitt was a dockworker on Bilbringi. In about 12 ABY, the renegade Jedi Dal Konur used the Force on him to prevent him from remembering Konur's presence in a hangar bay which Vitt was delivering some crates to. A group of spacers who were trying to find Konur later spoke to Vitt about this and he told them that all he didn't remember which hangar he had delivered the crates to or who had paid for them.
